description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Power HIIT Row' from the channel Nick Karwoski.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Hit short intervals at your sprint and max pace with Nick and Laine as you explore Miami.
